1
00:00:00,029 --> 00:00:01,370
Third,

2
00:00:01,370 --> 00:00:03,020
I'm sorry for everything.

3
00:00:03,020 --> 00:00:05,930
From here on out, I won't do anything you don't like.

4
00:00:05,930 --> 00:00:08,250
Do you have someone to edit your wedding presentation?

5
00:00:08,250 --> 00:00:09,610
Bone can do it.

6
00:00:09,610 --> 00:00:10,430
Sure.

7
00:00:10,430 --> 00:00:13,990
Everyone knows P'Un is chasing after P'Third.

8
00:00:13,990 --> 00:00:15,200
Wait, Third.

9
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:17,660
I have something I've been wanting to tell you for a while.

10
00:00:17,660 --> 00:00:21,110
If someone you love lies to you, will you forgive them?

11
00:00:21,110 --> 00:00:23,660
They are fighting! Let's go!

12
00:00:24,870 --> 00:00:26,910
You piece of shit!

13
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:31,800
What the hell are you doing, Khai?

14
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,320
