19
00:00:41,810 --> 00:00:43,320
Why are you so stupid?

20
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:46,282
You are stupid. He's not chasing after me.

21
00:00:46,799 --> 00:00:48,920
You are being fooled and yet you act like a big shot.

22
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:52,500
You're acting like a big shot. Why do you feel the need to defend me?

23
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:53,990
I'm jealous, asshole.

24
00:00:53,990 --> 00:00:56,891
- Why would you be jealous?
- Because I love you.

25
00:01:08,759 --> 00:01:11,240
P'Un, why are you doing this?

26
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,670
Want to be my arch enemy?

27
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:14,720
Get your act together first.

28
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:16,990
You idiot, I'm not chasing after Third.

29
00:01:16,990 --> 00:01:20,260
I'm not some 2-year old that you can fool. Everyone knows you are.

30
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:23,240
I think of him as a friend. Why would I chase after him?

31
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:25,640
P'Shane said you were.

32
00:01:32,270 --> 00:01:34,640
The cat is out of the bag.

33
00:01:37,550 --> 00:01:40,620
I was just messing with Khai.

34
00:01:44,689 --> 00:01:45,960
What the hell, Shane?

35
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,150
It's not my fault.

36
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:51,050
I was just trying to protect Third.

37
00:01:51,050 --> 00:01:53,570
Khai wasn't being clear.

38
00:01:53,570 --> 00:01:55,930
So, I told him that you were chasing after Third.

39
00:01:55,930 --> 00:01:59,440
Then, you could know what your heart wanted.

40
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:01,720
Do you know it now?

41
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:04,560
- What is Third to you?
- He's my friend.

42
00:02:06,140 --> 00:02:10,140
My brother. My family.

43
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:13,700
My guide. My everything.

44
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:16,110
Are you happy now?

45
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:18,020
Yes.

46
00:02:19,220 --> 00:02:21,600
You know what your heart wants now.

47
00:02:24,250 --> 00:02:26,240
It's win-win.

48
00:02:28,370 --> 00:02:30,220
Give him a big hand.

49
00:02:30,220 --> 00:02:32,220
Clap!

50
00:02:39,650 --> 00:02:43,400
Now we disperse.

51
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:21,750
[Theory of Love]

52
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:24,931
[Ep.10: Begin Again]

53
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,730
I'm sorry.

54
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:38,250
I did what I did because I didn't know better.

55
00:04:39,850 --> 00:04:42,170
Yeah, I know.

56
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:44,310
I've got no problem with you.

57
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:47,950
The person you should talk to is over there.

58
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:12,000
Third, can we talk?

59
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:15,460
What?

60
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:19,170
What kind of game are you playing with me now?

61
00:05:19,170 --> 00:05:21,360
Why do you say that?

62
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:26,280
When I said I loved you, I meant it.

63
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,950
I wasn't talking about that.

64
00:05:32,910 --> 00:05:35,380
It's about Praew.

65
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:40,070
I know that you and she weren't a couple.

66
00:05:45,610 --> 00:05:49,760
