67
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:56,780
I've known since the day I borrowed your computer.

68
00:05:58,050 --> 00:06:00,960
I saw the video on your Facebook.

69
00:06:04,969 --> 00:06:06,670
So, you were repulsed by me.

70
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:10,760
Yes, I thought I felt that way.

71
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:15,000
That's why I did many stupid things.

72
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:18,150
